summary "File System Library for the Lua Programming Language"
detail "LuaFileSystem is a Lua library developed to complement the set of"
detail "functions related to file systems offered by the standard Lua"
detail "distribution. LuaFileSystem offers a portable way to access the"
detail "underlying directory structure and file attributes."
